'''蜡伞科'''（[[学名|学名]]：'''''{{lang|en|Hygrophoraceae}}'''''）是[[担子菌门|担子菌门]]下[[伞菌目|伞菌目]]的一科，蜡伞科真菌子实体下的菌褶表面呈蜡状。

==下级分类==
* ''Acantholichen''
* ''Aeruginospora''
* ''Ampulloclitocybe''
* ''Aphroditeola''
* ''Arrhenia''
* ''Athelicium''
* ''Bertrandia''
* [[拱顶伞属|拱顶伞属]] ''Camarophyllus''
* ''Cantharellula''
* ''Cantharocybe''
* ''Chromosera''
* ''Chrysomphalina''
* ''Cora''
* ''Corella''<ref name="Lücking 2013"/>
* ''Cuphophyllus''
* ''Cyphellostereum''
* ''Dictyonema''
* ''Eonema''
* ''Gliophorus''
* ''Gloioxanthomyces''
* ''[[Haasiella|Haasiella]]''
* ''Humidicutis''
* ''Hygroaster''
* [[湿伞属|湿伞属]] ''Hygrocybe''
* [[蜡伞属|蜡伞属]] ''Hygrophorus''
* ''Lichenomphalia''
* ''Neohygrocybe''
* ''Porpolomopsis''
* ''Pseudoarmillariella''
* ''Semiomphalina''
* ''Sinohygrocybe''

